revisions.description: Removed references to unimplemented obects cienaCesTacacsClientGlobalAuthenticationPendingRequests and cienaCesTacacsClientAuthenticationServerPendingRequests.
Added cienaCesTacacsClientConnectionFailed to send out a notification when we cannot connect to a a tacacs server. Also added support for new IP types InetAddress and InetAddressType.

Deprecated cienaCesTacacsClientServerApplication, cienaCesTacacsClientAuthenticationServerApplication, cienaCesTacacsClientAuthorizationServerApplication, and cienaCesTacacsClientAccountingServerApplication, all of which were unused.
Corrected the range of cienaCesTacacsClientPrivilegeLevelAdmin from (2..14) to (1..13), and cienaCesTacacsClientPrivilegeLevelRW from (3..14) to (2..14)
